  "body": "The following reproduction:\r\n\r\n```go\r\npackage main\r\n\r\nimport (\r\n\t\"github.com/prometheus/prometheus/pkg/textparse\"\r\n)\r\n\r\nfunc main() {\r\n\tp := textparse.New([]byte(\"#\"), \"application/openmetrics-text\")\r\n\tvar err error\r\n\tfor {\r\n\t\t_, err = p.Next()\r\n\t\tif err != nil {\r\n\t\t\tbreak\r\n\t\t}\r\n\t}\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n...leads to:\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ go run main.go\r\npanic: runtime error: index out of range\r\n\r\ngoroutine 1 [running]:\r\ngithub.com/prometheus/prometheus/pkg/textparse.(*openMetricsLexer).cur(...)\r\n\t/home/julius/gosrc/src/github.com/prometheus/prometheus/pkg/textparse/openmetricsparse.go:47\r\ngithub.com/prometheus/prometheus/pkg/textparse.(*OpenMetricsParser).Next(0xc0000a2000, 0x1, 0x1, 0x4f819b)\r\n\t/home/julius/gosrc/src/github.com/prometheus/prometheus/pkg/textparse/openmetricsparse.go:296 +0x175f\r\nmain.main()\r\n\t/home/julius/tmp/fuzz/main.go:11 +0x93\r\nexit status 2\r\n```\r\n\r\n@yevgenypats You will be interested to know that this was discovered as the first fuzz-testing result by fuzzit (https://app.fuzzit.dev/orgs/prometheus/targets/promql-parse-open-metric/m6EqtgmNqwfLySMvwJNX) :)",
